  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_DE004150-221D-0135-BBBD-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Save</strong> button.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="moderate_quiz_for_multiple_students" data-step-uuid="F70AFC55-0CEC-4254-ACA7-CE42A434E0B1">
    <h2 id="moderate_quiz_for_multiple_students" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Moderate Quiz For Multiple Students</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/013/576/original/1493b0af-dc75-4224-bbbf-da1b12f19ab3.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/013/576/medium/1493b0af-dc75-4224-bbbf-da1b12f19ab3.png" srcset="" alt="Moderate Quiz for Multiple Students" height="558" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_DE007650-221D-0135-BBBF-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If you want to select multiple students, click the checkbox [1] next to each of their names. If you want to select all students, click the top checkbox [2]. Click <strong>Change Extensions for [#] Selected Students</strong> button [3].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="" data-step-uuid="79E43D95-DBBE-4B0E-B651-DA07E91BDAA5">
    
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/705/356/original/a4653055-ee2f-4a17-aab8-5a35471c1c0c.png" srcset="" alt="Give Multiple Students Extensions" height="461" width="496">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_DE00A6C0-221D-0135-BBC1-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Complete the extensions for the students you selected. Remember, depending on your quiz settings, additional quiz options may display for all selected students.</p>
<p>When you are finished, click the <strong>Save</strong> button.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
